reviewText: I love homeboy movies and this was a good choice to add to my collection. Not quite up there with Blood in, blood out or even Boulevard Nights, but I like Noel G. and I like to support the Homeboys that make it out of the hood and start living for Jesus.
THIS IS A REAL COOL MOVIE,IT WILL TAKE YOU IN A DIRECTION THAT WILL SURPRISE YOU.I REALLY LIKED THIS MOVIE ALOT AND IAM SURE YOU WILL ALSO.
